name: Coded Web Design
tag_list: web-developers, web-design, web-designers-ireland, e-commerce, search-optimisation, internet-marketing
overview:
Coded build websites for small to medium business and individuals requiring a proper online presence.

Coded Web Design have over ten years experience in developing sites for business and are agile and adaptive specializing in bespoke custom web development.

We work with clients all across Ireland, the UK and in the EU. Coded also takes on agency work for overseas branding companies and have acquired experience in building multi language websites as a result.

We work closely with clients to develop a proper web strategy for the client whether big or small. Our emphasis is on quality sustainable development and optimization delivering the best possible return on investment for the client.

Coded web design provide a range of SEO services as part of the planning for a successful website.

These services include; Keyword research and analysis, on page optimization and keyword deployment, dynamic sitemap creation and submission, web page submission etc.
